					<div>
						<pb n="13"/><p><lb/><origDate when="1517-06-16"><subst><del>Uff </del><add place="overwritten">Sur</add></subst> <subst><del>den</del><add place="above">le</add></subst> xvi <subst><del>tag</del><add place="above">jor</add></subst> <foreign xml:lang="la">juny anno <abbr>etc</abbr> xvii<hi rend="sup">o</hi></foreign></origDate>, en <choice><abbr>pnce</abbr><expan>présence</expan></choice>
							<lb/>de <term ref="lem017499.02">pourveables</term>, saiges et discretz <persName ref="per010068a">Anthoni
							<lb/>Villing</persName>, <persName ref="per010074a">Helbling</persName>, conseillieurs, <persName ref="per010071a.01">Ůlman Vogt</persName>, <persName ref="per010078a">Tschan
							<lb/>Reyff</persName>, <persName ref="per010072a">Willi Pugnioux</persName>, bourgeois, et <persName ref="per010073a.01">Peter Mertz</persName>,
							<lb/><term ref="lem014993.04">grossouttier</term> de la ville de <placeName ref="loc001060.04">Frybourg</placeName>, az <term ref="lem014868.04">regicqui</term>
							<lb/><persName ref="per009719a.01">Pierro Perat</persName> de <placeName ref="loc007669.02">Dompmartin</placeName>&#160;:</p>
						<p><lb/>Item az pris pour nourrir <subst><del>de t</del><add place="overwritten">ses</add></subst> enfans troys coppes
							<lb/>de blé a <persName ref="per009720a.01">Jehan Perat</persName>, son cusin, maix ilz les luy az
							<lb/>rend<subst><del>ist</del><add place="above">uz</add></subst> aprés en argent.
							<seg><lb/>Item az <term ref="lem015015.18">desroubé</term> une <term ref="lem014884.02">destralot</term>
							<lb/>qui valoit <measure type="currency" quantity="6" unit="Quart">six cart</measure> a <subst><del>u villaige de</del><add place="inline"><persName>Bostin</persName></add></subst>.</seg>
								<seg>Item luy
							<lb/>et ses compagnions, <hi rend="framed">l’ung nommé <persName>Jehan Richard</persName> de
							<pb n="14"/><lb/><placeName ref="loc007671.02">Possen</placeName>, de la parroche de <placeName ref="loc007669.02">Dompmartin</placeName>, qui vit, et <persName>Glaudo
							<lb/>Jacqui</persName>, qui est mort</hi>, allerent <del> leur tr</del> a <placeName ref="loc007673.03">Chapalla Vudanna</placeName>
							<lb/>rompre ung grenyer qu’estoit a <persName>Nicco Paysan</persName>, et la
							<lb/>prisrent <num value="2">ii</num> sack de bla <del>en ung chaulx</del> et trouvarent
							<lb/>une borse <add place="left margin" type="sign">au chaulx du bla</add>, et <term ref="lem016295.02">parsirent</term> l’argent qu’estoit dans icelle,
							<lb/>et en ehusrent chescung dé leur <measure type="currency" quantity="1" unit="k">ung escuz</measure>.</seg>
								<seg>Item
							<lb/>az faitz a murir dez <term ref="lem018923.05">beuffz</term> et dez <term ref="lem017507.02">vaches</term> par <term ref="lem014885.02">voudisi</term>,
							<lb/><subst><del>en</del><add place="overwritten">et</add></subst> leur <subst><del>donnant</del><add place="inline">az donné</add></subst> du <term ref="lem014886.02">pusset</term>&#160;; <persName><hi rend="framed">Jehan Richard</hi></persName>,
							<lb/>son compagnion, l’avoit faitz et luy az aprins a fayre
							<lb/>ledit <term ref="lem014886.02">pusset</term>.</seg>
								<seg>Item icelluy son compagnion luy disit <subst><add place="inline">qu’ilz</add>
							<lb/><del>que s’ilz le vouloit croyre ilz</del></subst> feroit qu’ilz seroit riche si
									<lb/>ilz vouloit <term ref="lem019541.05">renoyer</term> <choice><abbr>nre Sr</abbr><expan>nostre Seigneur</expan></choice>&#160;; adoncques ilz le <term ref="lem019541.08">reneyz</term>.</seg>
						<seg><lb/>Item fisrent a murir une <term ref="lem017507">vache</term> qu’estoit au lieutenant
							<lb/>de <placeName ref="loc007669.02">Dompmartin</placeName>, et luy <term ref="lem015635.05">bailliasrent</term> du <term ref="lem014886.02">pusset</term>, et son
							<lb/>compagnion <persName><hi rend="framed">Jehan Richard</hi></persName> luy mist en la gorje.</seg>
						<seg><lb/>Item ilz az faitz la <term ref="lem018102.02">gresle</term> atout une vergette blanche,
							<lb/>que <persName ref="per029416a">Rubinnet</persName>, son <term ref="lem019555.05">maistre</term>, luy avoit <term ref="lem015635.06">baillié</term>, et quant
							<lb/>ilz l’avoent faitz, ilz s’en allavent en leur maison, <subst><del>Item</del><add place="inline"><term ref="lem019457.02">volavent</term></add></subst>
							<lb/><subst><del>volavent per l’air</del><add place="above">per l’air en <term ref="lem014917.03">segnant</term> ladite <term ref="lem018102.02">gresle</term></add></subst>.</seg>
							<seg>Item son <term ref="lem019555.05">maistre</term> <persName ref="per029416a">Rubinnet</persName> parla
							<lb/>a luy au boix du <placeName ref="loc007674">Jorat</placeName>, sont environ <date dur-iso="P2M">deux moys</date>,
							<lb/>et luy disit qu’ilz ne vouloit riens plus fayre.</seg>
							<seg><lb/>Item quant ilz <term ref="lem019541.06">reneya</term> Dieu, son <term ref="lem019555.05">maistre</term> luy <term ref="lem015635.07">baillia</term>
							<lb/><measure type="currency" unit="ß" quantity="5">v</measure> ou  <measure type="currency" unit="ß" quantity="6">six</measure> solz, que devenisrent <term ref="lem018302.02">folliez</term> de boix.</seg>
						<seg><lb/>Item ilz ont tenuz leur <term ref="lem017043.04">secta</term> dessoubz du chastel
							<lb/>de <placeName ref="loc007669.02">Dompmartin</placeName>, au terraulx, et ly estoent ses complices.</seg>
							<seg><lb/>Item son <term ref="lem019555.05">maistre</term> <persName ref="per029416a">Rubinnet</persName> venoit quelque foys ver luy
							<lb/><sic>enguisa</sic> de <term ref="lem018315">chat</term> et en guise d’aultre beste.</seg>
								<seg>Item
							<lb/>ilz font la <term ref="lem018102.02">gresle</term> en une fontanne freyde, nommee
							<lb/>la <placeName>Freyde Fontanne</placeName>, qu’est dessoub l’<term ref="lem014907.02">abitaige</term> du
							<lb/>vicayre de <placeName ref="loc007675.02">Berchié</placeName>, <hi rend="framed"><persName>Jacquet Mermet</persName> de <placeName ref="loc007675.02">Berchié</placeName>,
								<lb/>lequelz az esté deffaitz <subst><del>par</del><add place="inline">et</add></subst> <term ref="lem019522">taillié la teste</term> par
							<lb/>le <choice><abbr>sr</abbr><expan>seigneur</expan></choice> de <placeName ref="loc007675.02">Berchié</placeName>, ly fassoit la <term ref="lem018102.02">gresle</term>.</hi></seg></p>
						<p><lb/><origDate when="1517-06-17">Sur le mescredi xvii jour de juing <foreign xml:lang="la">anno quo supra</foreign></origDate>,
							<lb/>en <choice><abbr>pnce</abbr><expan>presence</expan></choice> de <term ref="lem017499.02">pourveables</term>, saiges et discretz
							<pb n="15"/><lb/><persName ref="per010068a">Anthoni Villing</persName>, <persName ref="per010064a.02">Hanns Kromenstoln</persName>, <persName ref="per010074a">Jacob Helbling</persName>, <choice><abbr>consr</abbr><expan>conseillieurs</expan></choice>,
							<lb/><persName ref="per010071a.01">Ůlman Vogt</persName>, <persName ref="per010072a">Willi Pugnioux</persName> <del>und</del>, <persName ref="per010079a">Peter Dick</persName>,
							<lb/>bourgeois, et <persName ref="per010073a.01">Peter Mertz</persName>, <term ref="lem014993.04">grossouttier</term> de la ville
							<lb/>de <placeName ref="loc001060.04">Frybourg</placeName>, a <term ref="lem014868.04">regicqui</term> ledit
							<lb/><persName ref="per009719a.01">Pierro Perat</persName>, premierement&#160;:
							<seg><lb/>Que luy et ses compagnions ont <term ref="lem015015.18">desroubé</term> troys bichet
							<lb/>ou deux coppes de froment a <placeName ref="loc007676.02">Oppen</placeName>, en la
							<lb/>parroche d’<placeName ref="loc007677.02">Orsen</placeName> dessus <placeName ref="loc007618.03">Yverdon</placeName>.</seg>
								<seg>Item ilz c’est
							<lb/>aydé a fayre la <term ref="lem018102.02">gresle</term> entre la vaulx de <placeName ref="loc007675.02">Berchié</placeName>
									<lb/>et <placeName ref="loc007677.02">Orsen</placeName>, et <subst><del>c’est eut</del><add place="overwritten">ce fut</add></subst> l’<date dur-iso="P1Y">an passé</date>, et luy aydarent a
							<lb/>fayre <hi rend="framed"><persName>Glaudo Jacqui</persName> de <placeName ref="loc007669.02">Dompmartin</placeName> et <persName><subst><del>Gl</del><add place="inline">Jehan</add></subst>
							<lb/>Richard</persName></hi>, ses compagnions susdits.</seg>
								<seg>Item ilz fesoent a lever
							<lb/>la <term ref="lem018102.02">gresle</term> de la fontanne <subst><del>comme</del><add place="inline">qui</add></subst> ascendoit <subst><del>com</del>
							<lb/><add place="inline">et</add></subst> montave contre le ciel, comme ung <term ref="lem014887">chiron</term> de <term ref="lem014888.02">fin</term>,
							<lb/> et puis la segnavant per l’air <del>et volant</del>.</seg></p>
						<p><lb/><origDate when="1517-06-18">Sur le dixhuittiesme jour de juing l’an quelz dessus,</origDate> az esté
							<lb/>jugé ledit <persName ref="per009719a.01">Pierro Perat</persName>, que en tant qu’ilz avoit <term ref="lem018886.02">robé</term>, l’on luy
							<lb/>devoit mectre ung <term ref="lem014892.02">chevettro</term> au col et le mener au lieu
							<lb/>accoustumé pendre, et pource qu’ilz avoit <term ref="lem019541.22">renoyé</term> Dieu et
							<lb/>qu’ilz avoit faitz dez cas de <term ref="lem014885.02">voudisi</term>, ilz devoit estre mis
							<lb/>au <term ref="lem019528.02">fuz</term> et <term ref="lem019496.05">bruslé</term> cher et os jusques ez siendres&#160;; et feusrent
							<lb/><choice><abbr>messrs</abbr><expan>messeigneurs</expan></choice> qui l’accompagniasrent <del>cest</del> jusques au lieu out
							<lb/>ilz fust <subst><del>p</del><add place="inline"><term ref="lem019496.05">bruslé</term></add></subst>&#160;: <persName ref="per010068a">Anthoni Villing</persName>, <persName ref="per010064a.02">Hanns Kromenstoln</persName>,
							<lb/><persName ref="per010074a">Jacob Helbling</persName>, conseillieurs, <persName ref="per010071a.01">Ůlman Vogt</persName>, <persName ref="per010072a">Willi
							<lb/>Pugnioux</persName>, <persName ref="per010079a">Peter Dick</persName>, bourgeois, et <persName ref="per010073a.01">Peter Mertz</persName>,
							<lb/><term ref="lem014993.04">grossouttier</term> de la ville de <placeName ref="loc001060.04">Frybourg</placeName>.</p>
					</div>
				</body>
			</text>
